name: Air Canada 787-8 Dreamliner [C-GHPQ] Onboard Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Filmed back in 2015, Air Canada's first 787 is seen here touching down on runway 08L at Vancouver Airport after a 9 hour flight from Tokyo Narita. This was the second to last flight of the unforgettable Air Canada Foundation trip, on the plane that started it all! I will not be uploading the takeoff footage from Narita as the sun had already set. I still have a couple videos from Japan coming, so stay tuned for those. Enjoy this on-board footage!

Thanks for watching!
